<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhōng yú 迦南1006</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhōng yú dōu zuò zài tóng yī gè kōng jiān, zhōng yú dōu zǒu dào tóng yī gè qǐ diǎn.
 zhōng yú dōu mài kāi tóng yī gè bù fá, zhōng yú dōu zǒu shàng le fú shì zhǔ de shēng yá.
 zhè shì shén de zuò wèi, róng yào dōu guī gěi tā.
 míng tiān xiào yuán zàn měi zhǔ de gē shēng, jiāng huì chuán biàn tiān yá.
 qù ài měi yī gè hái zi, dài huí xuè tǒng de lǎo jiā.
 zhǔ bì jiā gěi nǐ lì liàng, nǐ bù yào hài pà.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1006</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>